title: A Witch's Welcome: The Swamp Witch Series
description: Book 2 of the Swamp Witch Series, A WITCH'S WELCOME takes you on a journey into a world filled with mystery, magic, humor, romance and delightful intrigue. Dan moves to Louisiana and he and Jamie begin to build on a their strange new relationship. Embarking on a new adventure with Jean, Dan lands in all kinds of trouble and you guessed it, Jamie and Tethys are smack dab in the middle of it. You will never believe where the Swamp Witch lands next!
author: Sonia Taylor Brock
